data.description: Here's a great opportunity in Stockton - a cleared 0.09-acre lot right in town. It's peaceful but still close to everything you need. You can build a cozy home or an investment property to best suit your needs. Set in the heart of the friendly Stockton community and close to the school. Plus, you're just minutes away from lake access. City water/sewer. Don't miss this opportunity to build your home or short term vacation rental in this great town!
